      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hamilton_(village)%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "The area that became Hammond was originally inhabited by the Iroquois League, and some land remains sacred to the Oneida Nation.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        4
